data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! Come check out this nicely built Brick Tri-Level Home. Hillside country setting, but within 5 minutes to Interstate 77. This home has a large yard with privacy. 3 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and a partially finished basement for extra living space. Large kitchen with island. Newly updated floors throughout the main level of the home (2022). Master bath recently updated in (2018).  New pump on well (300fft) installed in 2019. New garbage disposal installed in (2018).  New light fixtures and electrical ran in living room and bedrooms. This home features a beautiful brick gas fireplace. 12x20 sunroom addition. Generac Generator system. Outbuilding with electrical providing space for a workshop or  extra storage. Sellers will have the home professionally cleaned before closing. Schedule your private showing today!
